Initialise Server
. Install XAMPP
. Open Terminal
. Run sudo /opt/lampp/lampp start
. Edit opt/lampp/htdocs/index.php to point to desired Folder hence on 	
   typing localhost in browser will point to desired folder[/WebFolder]
. Open Desired Web Browser: Firefox/Chrome...
. Type in Address Bar: localhost(=http://localhost)[Check OK]

Initialise Sensor
.Connect uP with EthernetShield, LDR
.Connect uP to LAN Port, PowerSupply
.Start Arduino IDE
.Install Ethershieldeldo Library
.Upload bms.ino arduino server sketch to arduino board
.Ping Sensor IP Address from WebBrowser: [Check OK]

Sensing
.Open Terminal
.Navigate 2 Web Folder/sense=opt/lampp/htdocs/xampp/example/WebBuild/sense
.sudo chmod -R 777 WebFolder/sense
.Run ./sense.sh from terminal

WebDev
.Edit Contents in sda5/WebBuild/
.sudo rm -r opt/lampp/htdocs/xampp/example/WebBuild[=WebFolderLocation]
.sudo cp -r /media/sda5/WebBuild opt/lampp/htdocs/xampp/example/
.Reload Page on Web Browser[http://localhost]
			OR
.Open Terminal
.cd /opt/lampp/htdocs/xampp/example/WebBuild [Navigate to Website Folder]
.sudo gedit abc.php
.Reload Page on Web Browser[http://localhost]
			OR
.Try GitHub for Version Control, Code Distribution and Collaborative Editing
.Clone Online Directory to /opt/lampp/htdocs/xampp/example/WebBuild
.Edit pages in offline directory
.Test by reloading page on Web Browser[http://localhost]
.Upload to Git Repository, if Working
